---
title: Shepherd's Pie, Veggie Style with Mushrooms, Peas, and Roasted Carrots
description: Shepherd’s pie is best known as a meaty, stick-to-your-ribs sort of dish. But this recipe turns to mushrooms and sweet, jammy caramelized onions for a vegetarian variation that’s equally flavorful and just as sustaining. Rounded out with peas, carrots, and a blanket of mashed potatoes, it’s got all your favorite comfort foods packed into one perfectly pleasing pie.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shepherds-pie-veggie-style-41b7ead0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/shepherds-pie-veggie-style-72ac5b7e.pdf
